<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>189</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Kinepna deihum ka nei,
 Isun ei hehpih ziek;
 Pathien hinna ka luoh hi,
 Isun ei hehpih ziek.

[V2]
 Ka thagau veng intin,
 Ka guol danglam ngei lo;
 Tawpchanin ei veng ina,
 Lal Isu lopi pen hen.

[V3]
 2. Lau loin la kasa thei,
 Lal Isu min pak un;
 Ei panpih ding A nai zing,
 Lal Isu min pak un.

[V4]
 3. Ka zinna ah chieh zelin,
 Lal Isu mai muongin;
 Aw, ni chenga kipahna,
 Isu mai muon a hi.

[V5]
 4. Ka khuolzinna chieh zel ka,
 Lal Isu mai muongin;
 Chawlhna gam chu ka tun man,
 Isu kawma cheng din</lyrics>
<title>THE LOVE OF JESUS</title>
</song>